{"tid":639533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 房委會地盤鑽地傾側釀2傷　1人命危恐需截肢","createTime":"2018-04-23T14:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T14:45:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d92be67c2d26a244e972f03f8a0e4a07c8e6ee16","tid":639533,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/photo/bkn-20180423093908385-0423_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180423213221\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180423%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180423093908385-0423_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180423213221&h=ce7d5027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣深旺道近東京街西一個房委會建築地盤，早上8時52分發生工業意外，一部鑽地機由吊機吊落往鑽探位置時，突然傾側及撞向旁邊一個約5米高臨時工作台，工人爭相走避，其中一名36歲姓蘇工人走避不及，由工作台墮下，並被墮落組件壓着右腳。其姓王工友(25歲)見狀立即報警，消防及救護員趕至將蘇救出，他重傷昏迷送院。消息指，蘇由於右腳傷勢嚴重，可能需截肢保命，他現時情況危殆。另外，一名姓李(46歲)姓李工人在走避時扭傷腰，自行到醫院求醫。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkn-20180423093908385-0423_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180423%2Fbkn-20180423093908385-0423_00822_001.html&d=VN1ehRobdsX%2FTtqJnUt3LAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4ee8dfbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkn-20180423093908385-0423_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3bb766bbf57c8300768e7331d410a91bdb3dac55","tid":639533,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"none care <br />\n<br />\n唯有入嚟幫推post，冇咁肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d851a789ef52f7e103223b692052d8ffb5062e7","tid":639533,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb766bbf57c8300768e7331d410a91bdb3dac55","tid":639533,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"none care <br />\n<br />\n唯有入嚟幫推post，冇咁肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/f